                     <interp inst="t18150215-96-off585" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18150215-96-off585" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18150215-96-cd586" type="crimeDate">18th of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18150215-96-off585 t18150215-96-cd586"></join>, four remnants of muslin, value 50 s. the property of 
                     <persName id="t18150215-96-victim829" type="victimName">
                        Robert 
                        Hall
                     <interp inst="t18150215-96-victim829" type="surname" value="Hall"></interp>
